{"word":"εὔχομαι","slug":"εὔχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>εὔχομαι</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> pray (for),</b> of petition to the deity <b><a href='B:510 26:29'>Ac 26:29</a>; <a href='B:520 9:3'>Ro 9:3</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> 2 below for a more general sense of <el>εὐ</el>.); <b><a href='B:540 13:7'>2 Cor 13:7</a>, <a href='B:540 13:9'>9</a>; <a href='B:660 5:16'>Js 5:16</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in a diminished religious sense <b>wish (for), long (for) <a href='B:510 27:29'>Ac 27:29</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 2</a>;</b> some would here place <b><a href='B:520 9:3'>Ro 9:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐχή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:εὔχρηστος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}